    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean it's weird how you went from saying it was a \"victory\" and a \"moral imperative\" to saying it \"dismantled\" rights. it's like you're just flipping between two extremes. can you just explain the actual legal reasoning the court used without all the loaded adjectives?",
